Mungkin kita bisa memikirkan sesuatu
selama kita masih ada disini.

28
00:02:33,376 --> 00:02:35,439
Jangan bodoh.

29
00:02:35,584 --> 00:02:36,924
Kenapa tiba-tiba kau bersemangat begitu?

30
00:02:37,049 --> 00:02:38,576
Apa maksudnya?!

31
00:02:38,741 --> 00:02:41,112
